server
--------
apt-get install mysql-server git-core python-mysqldb libmodphp5 php5-mysql

git clone git://github.com/kclair/IS4C.git

* change apache docroot to IS4C/pos/backend

* update pos/fannie/define.conf with lane info

* python IS4C/pos/installation/install_server.py


client/lane
--------------
installed packages:
* git-core
* libapache2-mod-php5
* php5-mysql
* mysql-server
* python-mysqldb

run:
git clone git://github.com/kclair/IS4C.git
python IS4C/pos/installation/install_lane.py

edit /etc/apache2/sites-available/default for:
  DocumentRoot ... 
  DirectoryIndex login.php index.php

edit /etc/php5/apache2/php.ini for:
  session.auto_start = 1
  short_open_tag = On
  error_log = php_errors.log
  log_errors = On

edit $ROOT in pos/is4c/lib/initialize.php

http://localhost/configure.php
pDatabase: opdata
tDatabase: translog
